FBIS3-36821 "drsov028_a_94024" FBIS-SOV-94-028 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Feb 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Army Calls For Peaceful Solution to Dniester Problem LD0902161994 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1300 GMT 9 Feb 94 LD0902161994 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Russian 14th Army's Military Council has called on Chisinau and Tiraspol to search for peaceful ways to solve the Dniester region problem. The military council's statement notes that an extraordinary situation has taken shape in the region, and tension is being whipped up again. In the military's view, a solution can be found by implementing the Moldovan-Russian agreement on settling the conflict, which was signed in Moscow.
